lyrics:
[Verse]
Sweetness of coffee, honey's embrace, time's mystery unfolds,
Whispers of smoke, like silk they dance and they hold.
you'll slip away, from chains you'll be free (ooh-ooh)

[Pre-Chorus]
In the rhythm's embrace, you'll find your place,
Lost in the groove, in this endless space.

[Chorus]
Fire's pulse, whispers (then down, strikes),
Escaping past, to the sky we take flight (to new heights).
Guided by the city's beat, to uncharted realms you'll roam,
In our liberation, time finds a new home.
Now love unbounded, no regrets to deny (oh-oh-oh-oh)
